# Customer Churn Prediction

## Business Problem
Predict which customers are likely to leave a telecommunications company.

## Dataset
IBM Telco Customer Churn Dataset

## Tools
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-Learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Model
Logistic Regression

